oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Contest winners were announced at the Convention Banquet. All entrees were on display in the A. F .A. Booth.In order to do justice to the color print and slide categories, all winning color entrees will be shown in color, in this and future issues of Watchbird. This front and back cover shows the work of Dan Martin, Seminole, FL. In the near future we will show the work of John Krell and Pat Witman.
